    array('title' => 'The international cricket match', 'author' => '', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Sea songs', 'lyrics' => "\"The lists are op'd, the spacious area cleared,
Thousands on thousands pil'd, are seated round—Long ere the first loud trumpet's note is hear'd,
No vacant space for lated wight is found—Here dons, grandees, but chiefly dames abound.
