With eternity in view;
Bless thy word to old and young,
Fill us with a Saviour’s love;
When our life’s short race is run,", 'source_url' => 'https://gutendex.com/books/46041'),
    array('title' => 'Psalm 69:30.', 'author' => '', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Hymns', 'lyrics' => "Let every heart rejoice and sing;
