    array('title' => 'Asia.', 'author' => 'Emerson, Nathaniel Bright', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Folk songs', 'lyrics' => "The six marionettes, _ki’i_ (pls. VIII and IX), in the
writer’s possession were obtained from a distinguished
