Joyful he spoke: exulting cherubs round", 'source_url' => 'https://gutendex.com/books/409'),
    array('title' => 'A brighter world, and nobler strains belong.', 'author' => 'Wheatley, Phillis', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Love songs', 'lyrics' => "Say would you tear him from the realms above
