    array('title' => 'Or bathe his clay, or waste them on the ground:', 'author' => 'Wheatley, Phillis', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Folk songs', 'lyrics' => "Still do you weep, still wish for his return?
How cruel thus to wish, and thus to mourn?
