Latona ceas'd, and ardent thus replies", 'source_url' => 'https://gutendex.com/books/409'),
    array('title' => 'And rul\'d the fury of his flying steed.', 'author' => 'Wheatley, Phillis', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Folk songs', 'lyrics' => "\"Ah me,\" he sudden cries, with shrieking breath,
