And the hearts of Christ and the Christian
Meet there -- and only there!", 'source_url' => 'https://gutendex.com/books/937'),
    array('title' => 'Passed up to its God in His grace.', 'author' => 'Ryan, Abram Joseph', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Hymns', 'lyrics' => "A shadow! hast seen in the summer
A cloud wear the smile of the sun?
On the shadow of death there is flashing
The glory of noble deeds done;
On the face of the dead there is glowing
The light of a holy race run;
And the smile of the face is reflecting", 'source_url' => 'https://gutendex.com/books/937'),
    array('title' => 'As the hearts that met at Riverside.', 'author' => 'Ryan, Abram Joseph', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Love songs', 'lyrics' => "No cloudlet in the sky serene!
Not a silver speck in the golden hue!
But where the woods waved low and green,
And seldom would let the sunlight through,
