    array('title' => 'Joy reigned in the fullness of her grace.', 'author' => 'Ryan, Abram Joseph', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Folk songs', 'lyrics' => "The day was long, but ah! too brief!
Swift to the West bright-winged she fled;
Too soon on ev'ry look and leaf
The last rays flushed which her plumage shed
