French Flanders, which opens, like the Tuscan lullaby, with a short
narration:", 'source_url' => 'https://gutendex.com/books/36222'),
    array('title' => 'For example:', 'author' => 'Martinengo-Cesaresco, Evelyn Lilian Hazeldine Carrington, contessa', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Drinking songs', 'lyrics' => "Footnote 2, Page l (from p. xvii):
