The day declines to night                                       105
Lord, let us feel that Thou art near                            107
Come, praise with gladness, the Lord of all creation            109", 'source_url' => 'https://gutendex.com/books/29480'),
    array('title' => 'Penitence and Love--', 'author' => '', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Hymns', 'lyrics' => "Now, with my weeping would I cleanse my soul                    115
O God of love, on bended knee                                   117
O God, in mercy hear                                            119
