    array('title' => 'Turn out the hateful monster, sin, and let the heavenly Stranger in.', 'author' => '', 'year' => '', 'category' => 'Hymns', 'lyrics' => "Admit Him, ere his anger burn, lest He depart and ne’er return;
Admit Him, or the hour’s at hand when at his door denied you’ll
stand.
Yet know, nor of the terms complain, where Jesus comes, He comes to
